 2011-02522011-02-18,  AAFC,  ,  , 
ActFarm Income Protection Act
SubjectAgri-Recovery - Alberta and Saskatchewan livestock producers Assistance Program
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food to provide assistance through the Agricultural Disaster Relief Program under the AgriRecovery Framework to help livestock producers in the Peace Region of Alberta and the Northeast region of Saskatchewan in addressing forage shortages resulting from extreme weather in 2010.
